Hi Rachel,

The first thing to understand is that when we write something like 

  5r

it's just shorthand for 

  5 times 4

Next, take a look at

  Distributive Property, Illustrated
  http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/52842.html

and write back if it's not clear, or if you still have questions. 

Does this help?

